Name: INLOADER_ACC_FAIL
Description: Generated by InLoader when creation of an InReport for an incoming report has failed
ErrRepData: Packet identifier of report and identifier of reason for the creation failure

Name: INLOADER_INV_DEST
Description: Generated by InLoader when it receives a report with an invalid destination
ErrRepData: Packet identifier of report and invalid destination

Name: OUTFACTORY_FAIL
Description: Generated when an attempt to retrieve a report from the OutFactory has failed
ErrRepData: Type, subtype and discriminant of the report whose generation failed

Name: SNDPCKT_INV_DEST
Description: Generated by Send Packet Procedure when it finds an invalid destination in an OutComponent
ErrRepData: Type, subtype and discriminant of the report with the invalid destination and invalid destination
